dc_title_s: Plat book of Charlevoix County, Michigan
dc_description_s: Extent: 1 atlas (17 unnumbered pages) | Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners. | Notes: Earliest possible publication date determined from routing of highway M-66 to Charlevoix on folded county map.|Scale determined from section lines.|Includes folded map of Charlevoix County. | Scale approximately 1:51,000
